{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/BTFVR_GIF-1-Banner_600x100_V1.gif?t=1735922779\" /><br><br>Behind the Frame is a vivid, interactive fiction about an aspiring artist on the cusp of finishing the final piece of her gallery submission. Now available in VR, you'll be able to paint brushstrokes in a fully realized 3D space!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/BTFVR_GIF-2-Banner_600x100_V1.gif?t=1735922779\" /><br><br>A relaxing, eloquent experience that can be played at any pace. Become immersed in a panoramic world filled with resplendent colors, beautiful hand-animated visuals, and a smooth, easy-listening soundtrack. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/BTFVR_GIF-3-Banner_600x100_V1.gif?t=1735922779\" /><br><br>As a passionate artist, seek the missing colors that will bring your paintings to life - all while remembering to take the occasional coffee and breakfast breaks that keep you going. There is more than what meets the eye, for every painting has a story to tell.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318230/extras/BTFVR_GIF-4-Banner_600x100_V1.gif?t=1735922779\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Inspiration","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2318230/366af3738daf99aa4ab6ec744087f16ebb17755d.jpg"},{"name":"Turning Point","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2318230/2f80b2188367fd0be96d8ae13278bcc4120f30e5.jpg"},{"name":"Encounter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2318230/113ca3dbcdd9490676404356d1de4fe920f115c7.jpg"},{"name":"Behind the Frame","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/image